valgrind -v --tool=memcheck --leak-check=full --track-origins=yes <the program>

Add --dsmyutil=yes on Max OS X

-q: quiet, print only error messages
-v, -vv, etc: verbosity++

--malloc-fill=<hexnumber>
--free-fill=<hexnumber>
    Fill blocks allocated by malloc/free with the specified char (useful
    to test memory initialization errors)
